Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:45.87,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,This is the bullet used in the murder of Brigadier General Hughes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:50.79,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,.45 caliber, and only one shot was fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.79,0:01:54.25,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to say the murderer was skilled, but it was a close proximity shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:57.26,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,Not impossible for a woman to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.22,0:02:02.89,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,What is the caliber of your gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:05.52,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,.45.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:10.15,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,This is your ammunition request application.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.15,0:02:11.73,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:16.90,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,It's written here you only needed to be supplied with one shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:18.53,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,What did you use it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:21.28,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,As it says right there,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.66,0:02:25.16,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,I used it at Research Laboratory 5, while I escorted Edward Elric...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:32.25,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,But Research Laboratory 5 is closed down, and there shouldn't be anyone there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:34.04,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,But there were.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.04,0:02:36.55,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,...According to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:41.80,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,Should I order a search for this bullet you supposedly shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:46.97,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Research Laboratory 5 is in ruins now due to an unknown explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.10,0:02:52.98,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,So the place where you say you used\Nyour gun is usually unvisited by people,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:57.07,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,and even if we wanted to search for\Nthe bullet, it'd be under a heap of rubble...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:06.74,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,There's witness testimony stating you left the scene of the crime, on the exact date and time it occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:08.04,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:10.04,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,Compose yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:13.29,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,What were you doing at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:17.88,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,I was on leave that day and at my parents' house.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:20.55,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,You can confirm with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.34,0:03:26.64,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,Testimony from family members or people whom you are close with cannot be accepted as an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:31.73,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Second Lieutenant Maria Ross is currently being interrogated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:34.77,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Though you may be her superior, I cannot allow you to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.19,0:03:36.23,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:42.24,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Major Armstrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.66,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Sergeant Brosh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:46.74,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,You were here, too, Major?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:49.66,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Are you here for Second Lieutenant Ross?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:50.95,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The truth is-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:59.63,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, like the lieutenant, I also fired one round at Research Laboratory 5 while escorting the Elric Brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:00.55,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:04.30,Default,Brosh,0000,0000,0000,,I reported that, but they didn't listen at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.60,0:04:09.85,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,So they're planning on passing her off as the murderer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:26.37,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I look closely, you're really scratched up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.24,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Not an easy journey, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:37.25,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what are you going to do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:41.76,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:49.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:53.98,Default,Elicia,0000,0000,0000,,Mama, don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:04.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:09.41,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:14.96,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just that you've never asked me for advice about something concerning yourselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:18.33,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:25.97,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,It really scares me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:33.39,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you are fighting in a place so dangerous that Mr. Hughes was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:37.27,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I got really scared when I thought about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:44.15,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Because... you both could die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:47.65,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,And suddenly disappear from my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.41,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Mom and Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.08,0:05:58.50,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I got really scared when I thought about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:02.46,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I want you to end your journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:08.63,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I want you two to get your bodies back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.38,0:06:11.47,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't want you to go on any dangerous journeys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:13.35,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:16.52,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:22.81,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:28.28,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know what I want either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:32.78,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You're really kind, Winry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.78,0:06:35.20,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! W-W-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.20,0:06:38.04,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always kind!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:38.50,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&}PLACEHOLDER
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:41.42,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,Geez Al, what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.29,0:06:40.33,Default-alt,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! You're going to scratch me up even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:48.09,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.80,0:06:51.59,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Evening paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:53.01,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:55.76,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,What, the paper again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:58.23,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,I'm forced to watch over you all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.93,0:07:01.27,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,This is about the only thing I can look forward to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:08.61,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,Warrant Officer Falman speaking. I'm calling from an outside line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.61,0:07:10.57,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,Please put me through to Colonel Mustang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:13.03,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. My code is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:15.24,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.24,0:07:19.00,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,Airam, George, Oliver, 4649.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:23.75,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,It's that lady from back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Philosopher's stones...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:32.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ones who have tattoos of Ouroboros...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:35.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Homunculus...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.64,0:07:38.68,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How are they...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.68,0:07:39.56,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:41.89,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:44.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:46.77,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I... got this from the front desk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.94,0:07:49.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.11,0:07:53.61,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:59.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,"Second Lieutenant Maria Ross convicted on charges of the murder of Brigadier General Hughes"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:03.33,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:06.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the colonel or the major might know something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.42,0:08:07.88,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to tell Winry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain it to her later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:15.43,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:18.89,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Quit complaining. It's kind of like a collar for a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.22,0:08:20.97,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and I'm going to ask again just to be sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.97,0:08:23.23,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really fifteen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.73,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:26.10,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Stop lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:28.48,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,But it's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:31.48,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.44,0:08:33.40,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.53,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,An intruder!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:35.82,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Please lend us a hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:36.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:38.74,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better behave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:39.49,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:45.12,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Weak, weak, weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:47.75,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys even trying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.34,0:08:49.63,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.63,0:08:51.13,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Guns aren't working at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:53.38,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.38,0:08:54.01,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:56.72,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.60,0:09:10.07,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,But it's awfully boring not being allowed to cut them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:13.15,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Hello! Guy who's not affected by guns!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:15.20,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Could you let me out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:16.82,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.95,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,An illegal alien from Xing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:20.28,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:22.79,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Must have been a long trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:24.66,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you if you let me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:27.17,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to mess around with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:31.09,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,What country did you say you're from?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:32.67,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Xing of the East.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:35.80,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:36.97,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.39,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:55.94,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:57.82,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,I've finally found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.37,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,You were at Research Laboratory 5-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.32,0:10:04.29,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.87,0:10:10.42,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,I think of you every time I see the hole in my right hand you shot through.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.42,0:10:13.38,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Ms. Murderer of Hughes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:15.21,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,That's a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.21,0:10:16.59,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.59,0:10:20.09,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,The paper says it's confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:21.22,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:26.81,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, it looks like you're going to have the guilt pinned on you and get executed by a firing squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.81,0:10:27.60,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:30.56,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way... If they investigate thoroughly-
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:32.81,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Make a decision!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:36.82,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Get tortured to death by these guys or escape with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:38.15,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the two choices you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:42.45,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,That's horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.79,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Are those the only choices available?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:47.45,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.33,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,God, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:55.63,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, Dad, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:01.34,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll escape. Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:04.51,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better escort me, you stupid bone armor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:06.72,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you've got spunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.77,0:11:09.56,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Women have to have guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:11.77,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:14.31,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:19.69,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,Notify the entire city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:21.20,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,Maria Ross has escaped from jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:25.33,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,She's with a fiendish partner. Capture her immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:27.08,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,If she resists...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:30.12,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,...don't hesitate to kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:37.50,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,How much longer are we going to run?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.25,0:11:39.42,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and keep running!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:43.64,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Second Lieutenant Ross?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:46.55,Default,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Edward! Alphonse!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:50.73,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You're that guy from-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.14,0:11:52.27,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,And Ling, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:53.23,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Hiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:54.77,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:55.86,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's what {\i1}we{\i0} should be asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:11:58.61,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have much time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:05.28,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Lady, go straight down that alley to reach the warehouse district!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:07.28,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,It's dark enough over there to make your escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:10.16,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Second Lieutenant Ross, about Lt. Colonel Hughes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.16,0:12:13.25,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! If the military police finds you, they'll shoot you dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:15.08,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Second Lieutenant Ross!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.08,0:12:16.33,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Don't follow her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:17.46,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Second Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:19.25,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Second Lieutenant Ross!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:36.60,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You're Maria Ross, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.61,0:12:44.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.82,0:12:46.61,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so she did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.61,0:12:47.57,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.57,0:12:48.78,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.08,0:12:51.75,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:53.66,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,We're going, thin-eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:54.79,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:57.79,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Ling! Why are you working with a guy like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:59.54,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,We'll talk later!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.09,0:13:02.55,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:11.56,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Fullmetal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:19.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:22.69,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this, Colonel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:41.59,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.51,0:13:45.09,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lt. Colonel Hughes was...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.17,0:13:48.09,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why would Second Lieutenant Ross...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:49.89,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me in the first place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:58.14,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Attacking a superior?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.60,0:14:00.31,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Know your place!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:11.24,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,You can't, Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:12.24,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me, Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:13.62,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:16.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This bastard just killed Second Lieutenant Ross!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.04,0:14:16.83,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Second Lieutenant Ross?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:23.50,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, Colonel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.88,0:14:28.55,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,There was a kill-on-sight order issued for Maria Ross, an escaped convict.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:30.80,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:32.43,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,"That's all"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:36.02,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I do apologize for hiding Hughes' death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:41.31,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,But do not object to orders. Do not seek explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.15,0:14:43.31,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Simply obey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:45.57,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,That's what it means to be a soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:57.83,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel Mustang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:01.29,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,Explain the situation to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:06.67,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,There should have been a notice issued saying if she resists, we could gun her down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:09.59,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,She resisted, so I killed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:14.55,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,The Brigadier General was a good friend of yours from what I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:16.01,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:18.47,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,He was a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:24.11,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,It weren't your men who helped\NSecond Lieutenant Ross escape from jail, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.11,0:15:25.27,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:26.23,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.69,0:15:27.48,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.03,0:15:32.32,Default,Doug,0000,0000,0000,,So you could burn her to death like that yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:38.83,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I'd appreciate it if you didn't make assumptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:52.59,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,I'm truly sorry for not telling you about Brigadier General Hughes' death.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:56.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.10,0:16:01.77,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Don't brood over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:04.48,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,It is not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.69,0:16:08.15,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,So you're all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:10.40,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Nox...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:14.41,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,The damage is extensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:19.91,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,But from a scar on her tooth that was just narrowly left unscathed, we were able to identify her as Maria Ross.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:22.75,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,How horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:26.38,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Turning a babe like that into charcoal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:32.05,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,You must have really had something against her, eh, Mr. Mustang?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:37.89,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,Are you satisfied you were able to avenge your friend's death?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:48.23,Default,Nox,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me sick a hero from the Ishbal War\Nwould go so far against a little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:58.66,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Colonel, I can't express to you how sorry I am for what my subordinate did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.87,0:17:03.66,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea Second Lieutenant Ross would murder...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:08.08,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,She's always been honest... hardworking...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:11.25,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,And thoughtful...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:26.89,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're exhausted, Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.56,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Why not take a vacation?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:33.57,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Eastern Headquarters, where I used to be stationed, was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:38.74,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It lacks the bustle of large cities,\Nand most of all, there are so many beauties.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:52.55,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Mustang was able to avenge his best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.09,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,And everyone lived happily ever after.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:57.09,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,You petered out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:00.85,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't the purpose of this mission to make the colonel behave?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.85,0:18:03.51,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:05.89,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,The dog ate its bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:10.40,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,And it seems he's provoking people's antipathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.81,0:18:13.40,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,His own men may even be disgusted at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:16.28,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:18.53,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Request for leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:19.86,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,At this time of the year?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:21.41,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.12,0:18:24.49,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's fine. I permit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.33,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:43.51,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, for crying out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:46.81,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you leave this place?! There's no knowing what the colonel will say to me if he finds out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:50.52,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,No one saw me coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:52.56,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the problem here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:59.07,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,You're a poor soldier that's in the hands of a vicious criminal, so it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:00.53,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:05.37,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.37,0:19:06.62,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Sending a signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.62,0:19:07.79,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,Signal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.79,0:19:12.04,Default,Fal,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, why did you bring back some random stranger?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:14.67,Default,Fuu,0000,0000,0000,,Young Master! We've looked all over for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:17.09,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Oh wow, that was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.09,0:19:18.30,Default,66,0000,0000,0000,,More guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.55,0:19:26.14,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Elizabeth! How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.14,0:19:28.39,Default,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for calling all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:32.27,Default,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,But won't your scary aide scold you if you slack off too much?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:35.77,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! She's on leave right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.32,0:19:39.36,Default,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,Which is why I can call you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:41.95,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:45.83,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,This starts as soon as the lieutenant goes on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.49,0:19:48.41,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I guess she really was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.79,0:19:50.71,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,...His babysitter...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:52.25,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:55.54,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had any days off since I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.54,0:19:57.71,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm thinking about taking a holiday soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:20:00.72,Default,Eliza,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:02.97,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotten into fishing lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.39,0:20:05.60,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Want to come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:16.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:18.48,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:26.57,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do that all of a sudden, Major?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:29.33,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Edward Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:33.96,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:36.29,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Your automail is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.29,0:20:37.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.34,0:20:40.25,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. This is a serious situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:42.09,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,We must get it fixed right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:46.34,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,I'll escort you to Resembool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:48.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Well, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.22,0:20:49.39,Default,Winry,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.39,0:20:51.35,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We're going back to Resembool?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al, listen to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:59.23,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Alphonse Elric, you stick out too much, so stay in Central.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:02.28,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's make arrangements for the train ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:04.61,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Edward Elric!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.57,0:21:11.83,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Can you cut it out already, Major?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:14.16,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,No can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:16.00,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,This is also an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:19.50,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,From that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:23.30,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:28.01,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Major Armstrong and Edward Elric just got on a train.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:29.68,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:34.73,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Now there are no hindrances.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:46.15,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to come in contact with a witness who saw the guy who assaulted the prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.15,0:21:48.91,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,And this is what he looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.49,0:21:51.41,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he was alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:54.41,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he has anything to do with the Flame Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:21:55.71,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:58.17,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,But I think we can say for sure that there is a big possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.17,0:21:59.67,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he run off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.63,0:22:04.59,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's speedy, and to top it off,\Nhe's also good at hiding...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.59,0:22:06.84,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,So in other words, you don't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.84,0:22:07.88,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,You're so incompetent.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.88,0:22:09.97,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.97,0:22:11.47,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have enough people, that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.47,0:22:12.56,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,People?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.72,0:22:16.85,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,He's all we need.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.27,0:22:23.23,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,You're up, Barry the Chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.83,0:24:03.58,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The whole truth lies in Xerxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.46,0:24:07.59,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The residents left in the city that rusted away and disappeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.59,0:24:10.55,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,...wipe away the darkness within the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.34,0:24:15.68,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.68,0:24:21.48,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 18, The Arrogant Palm of a Small Human.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.89,0:24:25.77,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Humans, raise the signal of counterattack.
